the township now, sir.

7
00:00:50,799 --> 00:00:53,600
- How many do you have?
- Five.

8
00:00:53,667 --> 00:00:57,200
Only five?
By the time we got to the field,
most of the boys were gone.

9
00:00:57,267 --> 00:00:59,533
I need soldiers,
not excuses.

10
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:02,066
I will bring some more,
sir, I promise.

11
00:01:02,133 --> 00:01:05,433
Just bring them to me.
Youssou, take this.

12
00:01:11,166 --> 00:01:13,467
[ Machine Gun Fire Continues ]

13
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:22,033
[ Dubaku ]
You will learn
to fight like men.

14
00:01:22,100 --> 00:01:24,766
Of that I have no doubt.

15
00:01:26,700 --> 00:01:30,033
This... will make you
strong little soldiers.

16
00:01:31,133 --> 00:01:33,333
This will make you free.

17
00:01:38,133 --> 00:01:40,300
Come.

18
00:01:40,367 --> 00:01:42,133
Take it.

19
00:01:43,833 --> 00:01:46,033
Ah.

20
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:48,899
How does it make you feel?

21
00:01:49,899 --> 00:01:51,833
Powerful, yes?

22
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,033
Come.

23
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:05,833
Your mothers
and your fathers,
they have made you weak.

24
00:02:05,899 --> 00:02:08,066
But General Juma,

25
00:02:08,133 --> 00:02:10,667
he will make you strong!

26
00:02:10,734 --> 00:02:13,734
He will make you strong
so that you can take back
the country...

27
00:02:13,799 --> 00:02:18,166
from the governments
and the traitors
that work for them!

28
00:02:18,233 --> 00:02:20,766
- Like this cockroach, here!
- [ Whimpering ]

29
00:02:24,233 --> 00:02:26,866
Down.

30
00:02:29,567 --> 00:02:31,533
[ Whimpering ]

31
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:35,600
This cockroach works
for the government
and their white masters.

32
00:02:35,667 --> 00:02:38,567
- Yes. Yes.
- [ Man Weeping ]
No, no.

33
00:02:38,634 --> 00:02:41,033
Have mercy on me.

34
00:02:41,100 --> 00:02:43,833
They have taken our land.
No.

35
00:02:47,133 --> 00:02:49,634
But soon
all that will change.

36
00:02:49,700 --> 00:02:52,933
Soon all the land
will belong to
the people again.

37
00:02:54,467 --> 00:02:56,433
So...

38
00:02:57,467 --> 00:02:59,467
we must buy
our freedom...

39
00:02:59,533 --> 00:03:01,899
with the blood
of this cockroach.

40
00:03:01,966 --> 00:03:04,367
[ Whimpering ]
No.

41
00:03:07,866 --> 00:03:11,899
He's only a cockroach,
and you know what we do
to cockroaches.

42
00:03:13,133 --> 00:03:17,700
Chop up the cockroach.
Kill the cockroach.

43
